Rating: 4
This is definitely a keeper recipe! The only change I would make is to poach the eggs using the saran wrap method (saran wrap sprayed with cooking spray draped over a ramekin, crack the egg into the saran wrap,pull up saran wrap to make a baggie for the egg and fasten with a tie, and then put into the water for 3 to 4 minutes to cook).

